Name: Space Route
About the game: Space route is a game in which you have to control a space ship and dodge meteorites to get to your home planet, and you will only find out how long this journey will be in the game itself. Arrows Right, Left - this is the movement of the ship to the sides, and the arrow Up is responsible for the jump.
